data.title: Panoramic view of Valdosta, Ga. : county seat of Lowndes County.
data.meta_description: Colored with sepia wash. LC Panoramic maps (2nd ed.) 133.1 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. Includes index to points of interest. LC copy imperfect: Mounted on paper.
